      "supersedes": null,
      "contradicted_by": null
    },
    {
      "text": "As of 2024, Kuwait has a population of 4.82 million, of which 1.53 million are Kuwaiti citizens while the remaining 3.29 million are foreign nationals from over 100 countries.",
